---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "Privacy Policy — Nutri Swapper";
const description =
  "Nutri Swapper's privacy policy. We collect no personal data, use no tracking cookies, and run every calculation in your browser. Here's exactly how it works.";
const UPDATED = "June 9, 2026";
const EMAIL = "arnab47biswas@gmail.com";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} path="/privacy" localized={false}>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-[760px] px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-24">
    <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-mute">// Legal</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-[-2px] text-ink sm:text-5xl">
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-3 font-mono text-xs text-mute">Last updated: {UPDATED}</p>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-5 text-body leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Nutri Swapper is built to respect your privacy by default. We do not
        require an account, and we do not collect, sell, or share personal
        information. This policy explains what little data is involved and how it
        is handled.
      </p>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink">
        Information we collect
      </h2>
      <p>
        <strong class="text-ink">No personal information.</strong> There is no
        sign-up, no login, and no form that stores personal details on our
        servers. The calculator runs entirely in your browser; the ingredients
        and weights you enter are never transmitted to us. We do use analytics to
        measure aggregate traffic (see “Analytics and cookies” below), but we do
        not collect your name, email, or any data that personally identifies you.
      </p>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink">
        Local storage on your device
      </h2>
      <p>
        To remember your preferences between visits, we store two small values in
        your browser's local storage: your chosen <em class="text-ink not-italic"
          >theme</em
        > (dark or light) and your <em class="text-ink not-italic">language</em>.
        This data stays on your device, is never sent anywhere, and can be cleared
        at any time by clearing your browser data.
      </p>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink">
        Analytics and cookies
      </h2>
      <p>
        We use Google Analytics (GA4) to understand aggregate, anonymous usage —
        which pages are popular and how visitors reach the site. Google Analytics
        sets cookies and may process limited data such as a truncated IP address,
        device and browser type, approximate region, and the pages you view. This
        information is pseudonymous and is not used to personally identify you. We
        do not use advertising pixels and we never sell your data.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can opt out using the official
        <a
          class="text-link hover:underline"
          href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout"
          rel="noopener"
          target="_blank">Google Analytics opt-out browser add-on</a
        >, or through your browser's privacy and cookie controls. See
        <a
          class="text-link hover:underline"
          href="https://policies.google.com/privacy"
          rel="noopener"
          target="_blank">Google's Privacy Policy</a
        > for how Google handles this data. Our fonts are self-hosted, so your visit
        does not call out to external font or CDN providers.
      </p>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink">
        Email you send us
      </h2>
      <p>
        If you contact us by email, we receive whatever you choose to include in
        that message and use it only to respond. We do not add you to any mailing
        list.
      </p>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink">
        Children's privacy
      </h2>
      <p>
        Nutri Swapper is a general-audience informational tool and is not directed
        at children under 13. Because we collect no personal data, no information
        from children is gathered.
      </p>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink">
        Changes to this policy
      </h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy as the tool evolves. Material changes will be
        reflected by the “last updated” date at the top of this page.
      </p>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink">
        Contact
      </h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this policy? Email
        <a class="text-link hover:underline" href={`mailto:${EMAIL}`}>{EMAIL}</a>
        or visit our <a class="text-link hover:underline" href="/contact"
          >contact page</a
        >.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
